{ {THE PINK LADY}
A hundred years ago on a dark night a maid was savagly murded by the owner of{Bochyn Manor.}She was repeatedly and viciously stabbed with a dagger.Her back was terribly slashed and it was a slow,lingering death.
It is said that her killing was for no real reason and on certain dark,cold nights,in the stillness of midnight, she appears on the bridge laughing a screaching,piercing,haunting,laugh.
If you have the misfortune to be near Bochyn Manor late at night watch out for the{Pink Lady.}
